assay_description: Inhibition of RNA synthesis was measured as the concentration required to cause 50% reduction (in 1h) in 2-[14C]uridine incorporation into acid precipitable material using P388 cells
Inhibition of DNA synthesis was measured as the concentration required to cause 50% reduction (in 1h) in methyl [3H]thymidine incorporation into acid precipitable material using P388 cells
